"Choose" being the
operative word.

00:00:45.160 --> 00:00:46.870 align:middle line:84%
Catherine Austin
Fitts is with us

00:00:46.870 --> 00:00:49.750 align:middle line:84%
here again to share her
wisdom on how we can take back

00:00:49.750 --> 00:00:52.830 align:middle line:84%
our lives from the craziness
that is surrounding this

00:00:52.830 --> 00:00:55.480 align:middle line:90%
in the entire economic field.

00:00:55.480 --> 00:00:57.820 align:middle line:84%
I mean, everybody's just
sitting there glazed over,

00:00:57.820 --> 00:01:01.690 align:middle line:84%
